{"tid":728623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「歐盟」拒絕跟「中共」合作反撃特朗普","createTime":"2018-07-04T01:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T09:57:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"80c0be89f81b37aa074f448ed9d4e2c17278a63b","tid":728623,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:17:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.udn.com/news/story/6811/3233013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3233013&d=C4dbNeHLOq4e9TfxMsukGaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7afaf9e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.udn.com/news/story/6811/3233013</a><br />\n<br />\n北京施壓要求共抗川普貿易政策 歐盟回絕<br />\n2018-07-03 22:47中央社 布魯塞爾／柏林3日綜合外電報導<br />\n<br />\n歐洲官員表示，中國正施壓歐洲聯盟（EU），在本月稍後舉行的中歐高峰會上共同發表反對美國總統川普貿易政策的強烈聯合聲明，但遭到歐盟抗拒。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，包括國務院副總理劉鶴、國務委員兼外交部長王毅在內的中國高階官員，在布魯塞爾、柏林和北京舉行的多場會談中提議中國和歐盟締結聯盟，並表示願對歐盟進一步開放中國市場，以示善意。<br />\n<br />\n北京提出的其中一項提議，是中國和歐盟在世界貿易組織（WTO）發動聯合抗美行動。<br />\n<br />\n中歐高峰會16到17日將在北京登場。<strong>不過5名歐盟官員和外交人士對路透社表示，歐盟已回絕和北京結盟對抗華府的構想。</strong><br />\n<br />\n歐盟官員表示，中歐峰會預料會提出立場審慎的公報，確認中、歐雙方對多國貿易體制的承諾，並保證會成立一支工作小組推動世貿組織現代化。"},{"pid":"8a44d22f37d557f7d027429a105c5ee30527e4dd","tid":728623,"uid":42921,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"歐盟都千瘡百孔，同你支拿合作對抗美帝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abaeaa9959002f77ef262fef8203a270835756f","tid":728623,"uid":49215,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"中國憑咩施壓歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b96ada0485626c741d692b7a655594495f437e","tid":728623,"uid":83251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:21:14.000Z","msg":"本身歐盟都唔鋸大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d337969a9a5ab7cc02c5f737ae9c6190edd8db","tid":728623,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ef16bec87e191ab1aba3109b9c3e6831fe699b","tid":728623,"uid":57554,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"北京提出的其中一項提議，是中國和歐盟在世界貿易組織（WTO）發動聯合抗美行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐盟：下？你當年入WTO嘅承諾都未做喎，你搞掂左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7800a648dbfe361c4ae093696fe3353d2b54fec","tid":728623,"uid":26602,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b8b96ada0485626c741d692b7a655594495f437e","tid":728623,"uid":83251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:21:14.000Z","msg":"本身歐盟都唔鋸大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"一陣EU調轉同侵一齊搞支那就好笑"},{"pid":"680b46fbcba223a20fd8e1801099547ff644f1ba","tid":728623,"uid":39200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"贏國: 遲D你班友就跪住翻黎含我架, 2025啦, 同老美一齊等屎啦<br />\n(走住屌)"},{"pid":"55b364919e85d22f2aa7f28b31f1a127aa1e87bf","tid":728623,"uid":127611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"03dc4e1899fda4b26a21eaeda87668c2c8f80bb3","tid":728623,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"想同歐盟合作好簡單架渣，首先你要改善左中國人權問題先，如果唔係都幾難合作"},{"pid":"0b6a0a5f37437de2159ad999aafa0275ba90825c","tid":728623,"uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"班支國人成日想聯歐抗美<br />\n<br />\n根本歐盟同美國一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\